so ladies , pls be aware of this !! support homebased business !! majority of the homebased business are more WORTHY & CHEAPER !! they are MORE PROFESSIONAL than this physical shop 😑 #divalashandnails
some customers made a police report about the scam & yea they didn’t do anything about it. one of the customer went BLIND by the glue they used ?! some got their eyes severely infected !!

i went to see the reviews of that shop AFTER i did my lashes. ugh so dumb. i realised so many complaints !!! they’re scamming people’s money , POOR LASHES DONE !!! y’all can literally google #divalashandnails at facebook and see the amount of upset customers 🙂

SHE DID MY LASHES LESS THAN 30mins ?! WHAT THE FUCK 🤐 even those experienced ones would complete a volume set etc for at least 1hr onwards. leaving the shop , i was so upset cause one of my lower lash got stuck with the top lash. bloody hell sia 😑

i was using contact lens.( i use it everytime i do my lashes ) as she was doing my lashes , i could smell the lash glue so fucking strong. my eyes stings !!! 🥲 i was so afraid that my eyes will hurt when i opened my eyes. and it did sting for awhile and my eyes were slightly red

she then proceed to do my lashes , and bro .. she didn’t even clean my lashes. she didn’t even comb my lashes. she immediately put the undereye pad. she used a masking tape & do my lashes. throughout the process , it was a nightmare 😫
tryna scam my money pfft. okay moving on , she told me that the design for 4D Kim K won’t look very obvious since she’s using premade lashes. so i gotta change my design to 4D Cateye.

okay lol ? then i say “ oh then i’ll go with 3D “ HAHA she said “ okay la for u i give $40 “ PLEASE TELL ME AM I THE ONLY ONE WHO SEE THEM POST THE DIFF PROMO ON THE BLOODY SAME DAY ?!?!? https://t.co/owFIyESLKs

i told her it’s within my budget as i was expecting it to be $40. THEN , she told me it’s $45 for 4D instead of $40. i told her and showed her that it states $40 for 4D. she say that’s the old promo. the current promo they having is $45 for 4D.

i told her it was first time here. so she brought me into this small room. she showed me a menu & the price for 4D is $88 ?! she said it is a better quality lashes used. she compared two different types of lashes. for the promo , they’ll use premade lashes.

so i went to get my lashes done here. i saw the promo at their ig. 4D lash for only $40. hmm quite worth it and i thought it would be better since they own a physical shop. however , it’s terrible !!!!!

okay ladies , if you are considering to do lash extensions , AVOID GOING TO DIVALASHANDNAILS !!!! although it’s located at a physical shop , i would still highly recommend you to support homebased ones instead. PLEASE READ THIS THREAD !!!! AND HELP ME SHARE AROUND !! https://t.co/AE1y8S4RqD
